Detailed Description

cvmx_pcs::_rx::_sync_reg

Note: r_tx_rx_polarity_reg bit [2] will show correct polarity needed on the link receive path after code grp synchronization is achieved.

PCS_RX_SYNC_REG = Code Group synchronization reg
